# Google OAuth for Google Drive backup
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Create a project or select existing one
# 3. Enable the Google Drive API
# 4. Under "Credentials", create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# 5. Add your domain (e.g. http://localhost:5173) to Authorized JavaScript origins
# 6. Copy the Client ID below
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com
